Meet your newly reformulated Hyaluronic Eye Serum!

“Transform tired eyes with this refreshing, lightweight serum. It eliminates puffiness, smooths fine lines and enhances skin texture around the eye area for a firmer and brighter look!” - @curated.byval 📣

Now with double the Tuberose Stem Cells, clinically proven to brighten dark circles, reduce puffiness, and smooth wrinkles. Plus, multi-molecular Hyaluronic Acid to deliver deep hydration, while organic Cucumber Water refreshes and soothes tired eyes. 

It comes complete with a cooling steel rollerball applicator to boost lymphatic drainage and awaken your eyes.
